{"tid":1667132,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連登防滲透戰正式上線 一人一個三毛狗仔女","createTime":"2019-10-21T09:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T10:00:33.000Z","uid":335157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5881ec1af5925c1b6d81c836ac09e70ccadd04e","tid":1667132,"uid":335157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"連登有臥底唔係第一日嘅事<br />\n麻煩各位巴絲 upload可疑人士 and report<br />\n上至 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">IT狗(情報犬隻）</span></strong></span><br />\n中至 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">散仔(放工翻工收料）</span></strong></span><br />\n下至 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">狗仔狗女</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">希望大家可以做到<br />\n1.不封鎖<br />\n2.請檢舉<br />\n3.禁追蹤<br />\n4.善用不推文回覆</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日連登防滲透 由你我做起</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地絕對係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有系統</span></strong></span>咁搵其他<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">虛假</span></strong></span>消息<br />\n散播謠言 務求分化大家 <br />\n或者老點路線 比啲掘頭路 前線 <br />\n甚至老屈前線偷嘢 打平民<br />\n<br />\n大家遇到呢d post <br />\n唔該千祈唔好封鎖佢<br />\n反而係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">追蹤佢 </span></span></strong>加<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"> 不推文回覆 提醒各位巴絲</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係我遇到嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">狗仔</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開頭佢好似係我地自己友<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hevyQBC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhevyQBC.png&h=cbc30f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後尾佢話 後生仔屌鳩我地<br />\n根本有少少學識嘅中學生都唔會屌鳩我地<br />\n小學雞腦荀都未生埋 藍絲老師講兩句就信曬啦<br />\n<br />\n跟住就話<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打爛交通燈會<br />\n有交通事故</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實上係0<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>交通意外 <br />\n更加無手足因為交通燈出事</strong></span></span><br />\n基本上都係的士佬突燈鏟人<br />\n無論我地做咩都係有位比人入 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">劏肚破腸都比人話做戲</span></span><br />\n和平行街都比人話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">非法集會</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEXpXjp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEXpXjp.png&h=8d8b7075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住佢開始怒羞 露出馬腳 <br />\n叫人<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">曱甴</span></span></strong><br />\n除左對家/犬隻 <br />\n普通人根本唔會叫人<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">曱甴</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7hRaSTt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7hRaSTt.png&h=a65564b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEnding<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8r97U7M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8r97U7M.png&h=45204aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YC5GNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YC5GNN.png&h=c1a83d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em>對準目標</em></span></span>"},{"pid":"5c899ae2fb44b7e7a8648c5256ae31834a72ef8e","tid":1667132,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第十期牆紙］訴求在沉默中進化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=91e82fda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n歡迎投稿 : <a href=\"https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpadlet.com%2Flennonnewshk%2F6g5yp3tllkxx&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=1d5f0ddb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx</a>"},{"pid":"c2a26007d38ef34657afa14b99166ef415473e46","tid":1667132,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:48:55.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"2675303391d27a1459f36b2ac7b014fda80a8e1f","tid":1667132,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位宣傳一個idea。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1</a><br />\n[文宣升級] 郵差叔叔送信純熟將文宣迅速送出!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H03stW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H03stW.png&h=37a4782b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21f4bb20c7c2b23993274d98413e5f11ed300e62","tid":1667132,"uid":200450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:00:33.000Z","msg":"有個叫一鋪過 煩膠到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}